snippet: Thousands of people marched on Friday in the largest demonstration since protests erupted last year, calling on King Abdullah II to accelerate democratic change.
abstract: Muslim Brotherhood organizes largest demonstration since protests erupted in 2011, calling on King Abdullah II of Jordan to accelerate democratic change.
